[SN]TITLE[SN]
Driver in black 4x4 sought for stopping girl in Edinburgh

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man driving a black 4x4 car who stopped and spoke to a primary school girl in an Edinburgh street is being sought by police.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The young girl was walking to school on her own when the incident happened at about 08:40 on Friday in the Craigour area of the capital.
Police Scotland are appealing for witnesses.
The girl was unharmed and police said they are following various lines of inquiry.
